data.description: Located in the infamous Butterfield Meadows addition, close to Dyess Air Force Base, sits this beautifully constructed 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home. This offers an open floor plan with split bedrooms. The spacious primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom with a standalone tub, walk-in tiled shower, and great walk-in closets. The kitchen features gorgeous upscale countertops, lots of storage with the custom built-in cabinetry, tile backsplash,  walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances and an eye-catching vent-a-hood. Other features include: luxury vinyl plank flooring, updated lighting and fixtures, and wood beams in the living room to make the home more inviting and warm. The backyard is completely fenced and offers a covered back patio. There is also an attached two car garage. HCR Realty LLC does not give any warranty for its accuracy. Buyer is to verify all information. Buyer’s agent must be identified on first contact & must accompany buying prospect on all showings.
